[{"text": "Hey guys, Internet Historian66(6)420productions here.", "start": 1.32, "duration": 3.56}, {"text": "Before I'll give you another mediocre video...", "start": 4.88, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "Here's an ad!", "start": 6.68, "duration": 0.98}, {"text": "For Heroes Of The Spire!", "start": 7.66, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "Play it on your phone,", "start": 9.26, "duration": 1.26}, {"text": "borrow your friend's phone,", "start": 10.52, "duration": 0.82}, {"text": "then play it on the toilet.", "start": 11.34, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "It's an action RPG PvP OMG!", "start": 12.24, "duration": 2.74}, {"text": "Wow, hey are you playing Heroes Of The Spire?", "start": 14.98, "duration": 2.46}, {"text": "Excuse me?", "start": 17.44, "duration": 0.529}, {"text": "That's a yes.", "start": 17.97, "duration": 0.951}, {"text": "Build a team!", "start": 18.921, "duration": 0.699}, {"text": "400 is too many.", "start": 19.62, "duration": 1.62}, {"text": "*bing*", "start": 21.24, "duration": 0.5}, {"text": "Excuse me sir.", "start": 21.74, "duration": 0.86}, {"text": "Can you please turn off your electronic-", "start": 22.6, "duration": 1.48}, {"text": "NO! I'm playing Heroes Of The Spire!", "start": 24.08, "duration": 1.76}, {"text": "Oh, sorry sir my mistake.", "start": 25.84, "duration": 1.32}, {"text": "It got a 4.5 out of 5 on Google.", "start": 27.16, "duration": 2.16}, {"text": "How bad can it be?", "start": 29.32, "duration": 1.06}, {"text": "You can play as this guy.", "start": 30.38, "duration": 1.24}, {"text": "Opps! I should have blurred out his nipples.", "start": 31.62, "duration": 1.62}, {"text": "To see the uncensored version,", "start": 33.24, "duration": 1.32}, {"text": "You'll have to download the game.", "start": 34.56, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "EA was not involved at all!", "start": 35.86, "duration": 1.52}, {"text": "*yay!*", "start": 37.38, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "It even has a Reddit.", "start": 38.28, "duration": 1.04}, {"text": "Don't worry about that.", "start": 39.32, "duration": 0.72}, {"text": "Download Alliance from my links to get 50,000 dollar 50 gems.", "start": 40.049, "duration": 2.411}, {"text": "Thanks Konami!", "start": 42.46, "duration": 1.18}, {"text": "*Big Ben chiming*", "start": 44.66, "duration": 5.84}, {"text": "Hi there.", "start": 50.5, "duration": 1.12}, {"text": "It's me,", "start": 51.62, "duration": 0.72}, {"text": "JK Rowling.", "start": 52.34, "duration": 1.36}, {"text": "You know me from the series that inspired the Harry Potter erotica.", "start": 53.7, "duration": 3.88}, {"text": "And the ghostwriter for Tyler Oakley's autobiography", "start": 57.58, "duration": 2.32}, {"text": "*throwing noise* *thud*", "start": 59.9, "duration": 0.76}, {"text": "But I have another tale to weave for you today.", "start": 60.66, "duration": 2.64}, {"text": "And it's about spoilers.", "start": 63.3, "duration": 1.64}, {"text": "Flashback!", "start": 65.84, "duration": 1.36}, {"text": "2005.", "start": 67.2, "duration": 1.34}, {"text": "My 6th book is coming out soon.", "start": 68.54, "duration": 2.3}, {"text": "The kids are excited.", "start": 70.84, "duration": 1.84}, {"text": "The parents are misguided.", "start": 72.68, "duration": 1.88}, {"text": "And the hype is building.", "start": 74.56, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "*hype noises*\nAnd the hype is building.", "start": 75.16, "duration": 1.14}, {"text": "But the popularity of the series", "start": 76.54, "duration": 1.66}, {"text": "also had some unintended effects,", "start": 78.2, "duration": 2.2}, {"text": "It gave rise to four nefarious groups.", "start": 80.8, "duration": 2.56}, {"text": "(houses, if you will)", "start": 83.56, "duration": 1.4}, {"text": "The first,", "start": 85.26, "duration": 0.96}, {"text": "The Bootleggers.", "start": 86.22, "duration": 1.06}, {"text": "Making and selling knock-off merch.", "start": 87.54, "duration": 1.9}, {"text": "As well as knockoff books.", "start": 90.6, "duration": 1.42}, {"text": "The second,", "start": 93.54, "duration": 0.88}, {"text": "The Gamblers.", "start": 94.42, "duration": 1.14}, {"text": "Thousands of individuals.", "start": 95.56, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "Betting hundreds of thousands of dollars.", "start": 97.06, "duration": 2.06}, {"text": "On the outcome of the story.", "start": 99.12, "duration": 1.84}, {"text": "Who would die next?", "start": 100.96, "duration": 1.08}, {"text": "Oh! Fuck!", "start": 102.3, "duration": 0.58}, {"text": "Who would Harry hook up with?", "start": 103.98, "duration": 1.64}, {"text": "And the third group,", "start": 106.2, "duration": 1.22}, {"text": "The Thieves.", "start": 107.42, "duration": 1.14}, {"text": "One of them stole an early copy of the book.", "start": 108.56, "duration": 2.2}, {"text": "And tried to sell it to 'The Sun' newspaper for", "start": 110.76, "duration": 2.04}, {"text": "\u00a350,000.", "start": 112.8, "duration": 1.66}, {"text": "This was getting serious.", "start": 114.66, "duration": 1.32}, {"text": "So, the publishers started ramping up security.", "start": 116.66, "duration": 2.48}, {"text": "They put GPS trackers on all pallets,", "start": 119.78, "duration": 2.36}, {"text": "guards were stationed 24 hours a day.", "start": 122.14, "duration": 2.52}, {"text": "No one outside of a very small group", "start": 124.66, "duration": 2.26}, {"text": "was allowed to get their hands on the book.", "start": 126.92, "duration": 1.86}, {"text": "But despite the extra efforts...", "start": 129.52, "duration": 1.7}, {"text": "There was a leak.", "start": 131.9, "duration": 1.14}, {"text": "Which brings us to that fourth group,", "start": 134.9, "duration": 1.865}, {"text": "The Spoi Bois.", "start": 136.765, "duration": 0.655}, {"text": "They didn't care about money.", "start": 138.58, "duration": 1.52}, {"text": "All they wanted,", "start": 140.66, "duration": 1.36}, {"text": "was to ruin the fun.", "start": 142.02, "duration": 1.56}, {"text": "You probably know these three magic words,", "start": 143.86, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "'Snape", "start": 146.78, "duration": 1.26}, {"text": "Kills", "start": 148.04, "duration": 1.04}, {"text": "Dumbledore.'", "start": 149.08, "duration": 1.34}, {"text": "The spoiler started on a few small forums.", "start": 151.08, "duration": 2.16}, {"text": "And quickly spread everywhere.", "start": 153.24, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "And then it went from online,", "start": 155.28, "duration": 1.92}, {"text": "to RL. (Real Life)", "start": 157.2, "duration": 1.28}, {"text": "Teens were taking to their moms minivans and heading out to bookstores", "start": 158.92, "duration": 3.64}, {"text": "where queues to buy the Half-Blood Prince", "start": 162.56, "duration": 2.18}, {"text": "was stretched around the block.", "start": 164.74, "duration": 1.82}, {"text": "But that wasn't all.", "start": 177.76, "duration": 1.24}, {"text": "They started printing custom shirts,", "start": 179.0, "duration": 2.08}, {"text": "posters,", "start": 181.62, "duration": 0.92}, {"text": "even car enthusiasts were getting in on the action.", "start": 182.54, "duration": 2.74}, {"text": "Spoilers, get it?", "start": 185.28, "duration": 1.18}, {"text": "But worst hit of all,", "start": 187.04, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "with the sacred Potter forums,", "start": 188.54, "duration": 2.36}, {"text": "people were making accounts there and posting spoilers in every thread.", "start": 190.9, "duration": 3.7}, {"text": "I couldn't bear to watch...", "start": 195.18, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But there was an even bigger event on the horizon.", "start": 198.22, "duration": 2.56}, {"text": "The final book in the series,", "start": 201.46, "duration": 2.12}, {"text": "and this would contain", "start": 203.58, "duration": 1.94}, {"text": "the greatest spoilers of all.", "start": 205.52, "duration": 2.96}, {"text": "Fast-forward to 2007,", "start": 210.36, "duration": 1.88}, {"text": "it's getting worse.", "start": 212.24, "duration": 1.34}, {"text": "There's now a 5th group,", "start": 213.58, "duration": 1.32}, {"text": "Journalists.", "start": 214.9, "duration": 0.66}, {"text": "Who are rummaging through my trash", "start": 215.56, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "looking for scraps of paper.", "start": 217.36, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "We started taking it", "start": 219.32, "duration": 1.16}, {"text": "viry siriously.", "start": 220.48, "duration": 1.28}, {"text": "More GPS trackers,", "start": 222.08, "duration": 1.44}, {"text": "more guards.", "start": 223.52, "duration": 1.62}, {"text": "We made fake endings", "start": 225.14, "duration": 1.36}, {"text": "We even got the GCHQ involved", "start": 231.84, "duration": 2.02}, {"text": "to conduct surveillance on some of those first 3 groups.", "start": 233.86, "duration": 3.02}, {"text": "We did everything we possibly could from my precious book.", "start": 237.16, "duration": 4.44}, {"text": "And yet.", "start": 242.84, "duration": 0.96}, {"text": "The retailer DeepDiscount.com", "start": 245.88, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "sent the bloody thing out to customers a week early.", "start": 247.98, "duration": 2.86}, {"text": "And The Spoi Bois,", "start": 251.92, "duration": 1.84}, {"text": "were more prepared", "start": 253.76, "duration": 1.36}, {"text": "and organized", "start": 255.12, "duration": 1.18}, {"text": "than ever.", "start": 256.3, "duration": 0.74}, {"text": "July 18th,", "start": 258.16, "duration": 1.72}, {"text": "they called it,", "start": 259.88, "duration": 0.88}, {"text": "'P-Day'.", "start": 260.76, "duration": 0.78}, {"text": "Because they're not that creative.", "start": 262.12, "duration": 1.76}, {"text": "Attacks on the shores of the United States.", "start": 264.54, "duration": 2.26}, {"text": "Attacks in the streets of London.", "start": 287.96, "duration": 2.2}, {"text": "And everywhere else, too.", "start": 301.6, "duration": 1.72}, {"text": "World of Warcraft,", "start": 303.82, "duration": 1.54}, {"text": "Furcadia", "start": 305.36, "duration": 1.02}, {"text": "more shirts,", "start": 306.38, "duration": 1.12}, {"text": "posters with bolder font,", "start": 307.5, "duration": 1.72}, {"text": "more cars,", "start": 309.22, "duration": 1.14}, {"text": "even a shitty cake.", "start": 310.36, "duration": 1.44}, {"text": "A few people even made a massive banner", "start": 312.9, "duration": 2.08}, {"text": "and hung it over the motorway to ruin it for morning commuters.", "start": 314.98, "duration": 3.18}, {"text": "They were stopped by police thankfully.", "start": 318.16, "duration": 1.7}, {"text": "But the hardest hit of all,", "start": 321.08, "duration": 1.68}, {"text": "again,", "start": 322.76, "duration": 0.72}, {"text": "was the sacred Potter forums.", "start": 324.26, "duration": 1.92}, {"text": "2:30AM Eastern Standard Time,", "start": 327.52, "duration": 2.18}, {"text": "someone managed to get access to the site admin.", "start": 329.7, "duration": 2.32}, {"text": "They wrote a message with every single spoiler in it.", "start": 332.84, "duration": 2.98}, {"text": "Set recipients to all.", "start": 336.98, "duration": 1.26}, {"text": "And hit send.", "start": 339.1, "duration": 1.1}, {"text": "Everyone registered to the site,", "start": 340.74, "duration": 2.02}, {"text": "thousands of the most dedicated fans,", "start": 342.76, "duration": 2.48}, {"text": "*You got mail!*", "start": 345.24, "duration": 0.96}, {"text": "received the email.", "start": 346.2, "duration": 1.9}, {"text": "The only thing they could do", "start": 348.1, "duration": 1.48}, {"text": "was temporarily close down the forum.", "start": 349.58, "duration": 2.12}, {"text": "And that brings us to why I'm telling you all this.", "start": 353.4, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Because there were always supposed to be 8 books in the series", "start": 357.76, "duration": 3.54}, {"text": "And now you'll never get to read the final installment.", "start": 361.86, "duration": 3.38}, {"text": "Harry Potter And The Unbelievable Plot Twists That Change Everything", "start": 365.8, "duration": 4.2}, {"text": "Because you couldn't keep your mouth shut.", "start": 371.14, "duration": 2.7}, {"text": "Now if you'll excuse me,", "start": 375.22, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "it's tea time at my private moon castle.", "start": 376.72, "duration": 2.32}, {"text": "*5*", "start": 379.04, "duration": 1.06}, {"text": "Toodaloo!\n*4*", "start": 380.1, "duration": 1.34}, {"text": "*3*", "start": 381.44, "duration": 1.34}, {"text": "*2*", "start": 382.78, "duration": 1.28}, {"text": "*1*", "start": 384.06, "duration": 1.58}, {"text": "We have ignition.", "start": 385.64, "duration": 1.98}]